OL,6,FA serial rapist who hid camera devices
OL,7,Finside air fresheners to film his
OL,8,Fcrimes has been jailed for life.
OL,10,FChao Xu, 33, of Greenwich, south-east
OL,11,FLondon, pleaded guilty in August to 24
OL,12,Fsexual offences over the course of
OL,13,Fthree years, including rape, sexual
OL,14,Fassault and upskirting.
OL,16,FOn Friday, he was sentenced to life in
OL,17,Fprison with a minimum term of 14 years
OL,18,Fat Woolwich Crown Court.
